Class ProjectStringMap

java.lang.Object
  org.hackystat.sensorbase.resource.projects.ProjectStringMap

public class ProjectStringMap
extends java.lang.Object

Helper class to support Project to String mappings. We need this I don't know how to define JAXB Project instances with a custom equals() and hashCode() method such that equal Project instances are those with the same name and owner.
